Class StudentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • StudentList

  • public class StudentList
extends java.lang.Object
    The container StudentList class which holds an array of students that has methods add, remove, and find specific students. The array is initially size GROW_SIZE and grows by GROW_SIZE every time we run out of space. Removed item is replaced by the last item of the array.
